
  1. create bool sorted init as false;
  2. create while loop with condition !sorted
  3. set sorted to true
  3. create for loop to cycle through all elements of array
  4. compare array[i] and array[i+1]
  5. if compare is true, swap elements
    a. save array[i] to new variable
    b. assign array[i] to array[i+1]
    c. assign array[i+1] to save variable
    d. set sorted to false
  6. else it will exit loop with sorted list
  